node.text: Before I was a model or even thought I could be, I wanted to be a journalist and presenter.. God has blessed my career that I can do things I dreamt of along with the things I could’ve Never dreamt of 🍾✨ (also happy birthday @damsonidris we rang in ur birthday right😂) 🎥 @marcusarjon

node.text: Thank you to everyone who came out to celebrate my PLT collection! We really brought Jamaica to Los Angeles last night! 🇯🇲❤️🔥 Thank you to my friends @jackharlow @offsetyrn @dojacat @breerunway who performed and turned the spot up! Thank you @djsugashay @casanovaiam @zackbia for dj-ing and bring the vibes! @wifeoftheparty @umarkamani @acsimon y’all did the damn thing with this one!!!!! ❤️🙏🏽 🎥 @byjamiebruce

node.text: I’m literally crying right now 🥺😭 I couldn’t be in Toronto to celebrate the launch of my global @Puma campaign with my family so puma gave them a special day Downtown to see me up on the big screens. How beautiful is this 😭😍 seeing my mom and my grandparents so proud of their little girl is what really makes everything worth it. Thank you to my @pumasportstyle family for putting this all together and making my family feel so special! I know this is a moment they will never forget! ❤️🥰

node.text: So Kelvin is this incredible artist who’s work I’ve loved for some time! He reached out to me and asked if he could draw me to go to auction for the charity of my choice. What an honour to be captured by this talented amazing soul! Thank you Kelvin for sharing your amazing talents with the world 😇🎨🦋💛
